  "text": "Jerkiness and fluidity, then, can contribute to the analysis and recognition of expressive movement qualities, particularly in multimodal frameworks that involve multiple descriptors and sensing modalities [CITATION_1] . However, it is important to emphasize that Laban effort elements are qualitative \"inner attitudes\" of a person moving towards the effort factor. Using computable descriptors should not be seen as an attempt to quantitatively measure the effort qualities but rather as a means to aid in the design of computational models capable of discerning and recognizing different expressive movement behaviors.",
